OL,3,CGovernment calls on broadband
OL,4,Ccompanies to limit installation of
OL,5,Ctelegraph poles
OL,7,FThe Government has called on broadband
OL,8,Fcompanies to limit the installation of
OL,9,Funnecessary telegraph poles, saying it
OL,10,Fwill bring in legislation to prevent
OL,11,Fthem if the industry fails to comply.
OL,13,FTechnology minister Sir Chris Bryant
OL,14,Fsaid the Government's support for the
OL,15,Frollout of fast broadband across the
OL,16,FUK is "unwavering", but that the
OL,17,Findustry should be "mindful" of the
OL,18,Fconcerns of communities when
OL,19,Finstalling infrastructure.
