OL,4,Ccompanies to limit installation of
OL,5,Ctelegraph poles
OL,7,FEarlier this year, the Bournville
OL,8,FVillage Trust, which manages the
OL,9,Fpicturesque estate in Birmingham, said
OL,10,Fit would consider legal action after a
OL,11,Fnumber of telegraph poles appeared in
OL,12,Fthe village.
OL,14,FTelecom companies are required to give
OL,15,Fnotice to the local planning authority
OL,16,Fand residents before installing a
OL,17,Fpole, but are not required to obtain
OL,18,Fplanning permission because the poles
OL,19,Fare classed as permitted developments.
