OL,3,CGovernment calls on broadband
OL,4,Ccompanies to limit installation of
OL,5,Ctelegraph poles
OL,7,FThe Government is urging companies to
OL,8,Fshare existing infrastructure where
OL,9,Fpossible or place them underground,
OL,10,Finstead of installing new poles for
OL,11,Fbroadband cables.
OL,13,FIn a letter to operators, Sir Chris
OL,14,Furged them to revise the Code of
OL,15,FPractice when it comes to installing
OL,16,Ftelegraph poles.
OL,18,FHe said he will not shy away from
OL,19,Fchanging the law, should the industry
OL,20,Ffail to listen to communities.
