OL,3,CGovernment calls on broadband
OL,4,Ccompanies to limit installation of
OL,5,Ctelegraph poles
OL,7,FSir Chris said: "Our dedication to
OL,8,Frolling out fast and reliable
OL,9,Fbroadband across the country is
OL,10,Funwavering.
OL,12,F"But this must happen in a way that is
OL,13,Fmindful of local communities, many of
OL,14,Fwhom have expressed dismay when their
OL,15,Froad is dug up yet again or yet
OL,16,Fanother telegraph pole appears in
OL,17,Ftheir street.
