OL,3,CGovernment calls on broadband
OL,4,Ccompanies to limit installation of
OL,5,Ctelegraph poles
OL,7,F"This is why I'm calling on telecoms
OL,8,Fcompanies to prioritise the sharing of
OL,9,Finfrastructure and take into account
OL,10,Fthe views of residents and businesses
OL,11,Fin rural areas.
OL,13,F"By doing so, we can bring the
OL,14,Fadvantages of high-speed internet to
OL,15,Fall corners of the nation more rapidly
OL,16,Fand responsibly, while minimising
OL,17,Fdisruptive ground digging and ending
OL,18,Fthe installation of unnecessary
OL,19,Ftelegraph poles, ensuring communities'
OL,20,Fconcerns are not overlooked."
