OL,7,FThe Government is to hold a round-
OL,8,Ftable meeting with telecom companies
OL,9,Fin September to discuss issues raised
OL,10,Fby the public and encourage greater
OL,11,Fcollaboration.
OL,13,FAn Openreach spokesperson said: "The
OL,14,FUK is undergoing a digital
OL,15,Ftransformation, to world-class full-
OL,16,Ffibre broadband.
