OL,3,CGovernment calls on broadband
OL,4,Ccompanies to limit installation of
OL,5,Ctelegraph poles
OL,7,F"To help companies build out their
OL,8,Fnetworks, we offer access to our
OL,9,Fnational network of poles and
OL,10,Funderground ducts. To date over 100
OL,11,Fcompanies are making use of our ducts
OL,12,Fand poles, and it's enabled them to
OL,13,Fconnect nearly 900,000 of their
OL,14,Fcustomers.
