OL,3,CGovernment calls on broadband
OL,4,Ccompanies to limit installation of
OL,5,Ctelegraph poles
OL,7,F"We welcome greater collaboration
OL,8,Fwithin the industry and believe all
OL,9,Fnetwork builders should offer access
OL,10,Fon comparable terms to us, thereby
OL,11,Freducing the need for new poles and
OL,12,Fduct in certain areas. However, there
OL,13,Fwill be a need for new infrastructure
OL,14,Fto ensure some premises aren't left
OL,15,Fbehind.
OL,17,F"We're looking forward to working with
OL,18,FGovernment to ensure the digital
OL,19,Ftransformation of the UK continues at
OL,20,Fpace, which will include improved
OL,21,Finfrastructure sharing."
